            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li>Excelerate Energy (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/EE\" title=\"Excelerate Energy, Inc.\">EE</a></span>) <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20337579-excelerate-energy-announces-share-repurchase-authorization\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"announced\">announced</a> on Thursday that it has approved a new share repurchase authorization of up to $75M of its Class A common shares.</li>\n<li>Under the program, repurchases can be made by open market purchases, block trades, privately negotiated transactions, and non-discretionary trading plans, all in compliance with the rules of the SEC.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
